Penny Stock notes:
Easy to borrow penny stocks (so people will short)
Good news catalyst
Low float
Low outstanding shares
1. 1:10 - Abnormal Volume
2. 4:27 - Association w/Big Name Institutional Investors
3. 5:50 - Spike-ability - cause of previous spikes
4. 6:55 - Previous Spike History
5. 8:00 - Catalyst(News-Charlie prefers bio-tech catalyst because they have known dates.)
